                        <note rend="inline" type="source">882.5048/32: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of
                                    State</gloss> to the Minister in Liberia</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Francis</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1929-06-19T17:00:00-04:00">June 19, 1929—5
                                p.m.</date></dateline></opener>
                        <p>10. Your 19, June 18, 2 p.m. Your course of action meets with the
                            Department’s approval.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Clark</hi></signed></closer>
